_:Ne81d3c8d350043f99d4ac6cb978fe71f <http://schema.org/description> "The Treasure Valuation Committee (TVC), comprising of independent antiques or coin experts and a representative of the hobby of metal-detecting, establishes the likely market value of each treasure find. A reward of this value can then be made to the finders of treasure and to the owners of find sites unless there are grounds for no reward or a reduced award to be made. TVC is an advisory non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Department for Culture, Media and Sport ." .
